---
// About/Bio section
---

<section id='about' class='min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-ew-red-dark/20 to-black py-20 px-4'>
	<div class='container mx-auto max-w-4xl'>
		<h2 class='text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-ew-red-light mb-16 text-center'>
			<span class='inline-block' style='text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 82, 82, 0.5);'>Bio</span>
		</h2>

		<div class='bg-black/50 border-2 border-ew-red/30 p-4 md:p-8 lg:p-12 backdrop-blur-sm'>
			<div class='prose prose-invert max-w-none'>
				<p class='text-ew-cream/90 leading-relaxed mb-6'>
					Jyväskylä-based metal collective In Thorns released their debut album "the last bead on a cord of songs" in January 2024, earning Newcomer of the Year 2024 recognition in Kaaoszine readers' poll. This experienced lineup is ready to bring their uncompromising show to stages with full intensity and passion.
				</p>

				<p class='text-ew-cream/90 leading-relaxed mb-6'>
					The collective creates metal driven by crushing soundscapes, nihilistic and darkly poetic lyrics, and soaring melodies. Drawing inspiration from surrealist art and modern horror, In Thorns delivers an immersive sonic experience that balances devastating heaviness with haunting beauty.
				</p>

				<h3 class='text-2xl text-ew-orange mt-8 mb-4'>Members</h3>
				<ul class='text-ew-cream/80 space-y-2 list-none pl-0'>
					<li class='border-l-2 border-ew-orange/50 pl-4'>Kristian Ruutala (harsh vocals)</li>
					<li class='border-l-2 border-ew-orange/50 pl-4'>Aleksi Statsevich (harsh vocals)</li>
					<li class='border-l-2 border-ew-orange/50 pl-4'>Aavee Tikkanen (vocals/guitar)</li>
					<li class='border-l-2 border-ew-orange/50 pl-4'>Aleksi Ruotsalainen (guitar)</li>
					<li class='border-l-2 border-ew-orange/50 pl-4'>Jimi Kinnunen (drums)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
